<div class="bbm-modal__topbar">
  <h3 class="bbm-modal__title">比赛结束</h3>
</div>
<div class="bbm-modal__section">
  <h1>{{winner}} 赢得比赛!</h1>
  <div class="score-board">
    <div class="col-xs-12 score-row">
      <div class="col-xs-4 {{#if p1_win_1}}win-game{{/if}}">{{p1_1}}</div>
      <div class="col-xs-4 {{#if p1_win_2}}win-game{{/if}}">{{p1_2}}</div>
      <div class="col-xs-4 {{#if p1_win_3}}win-game{{/if}}">{{p1_3}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 score-row">
      <div class="col-xs-4 {{#if p2_win_1}}win-game{{/if}}">{{p2_1}}</div>
      <div class="col-xs-4 {{#if p2_win_2}}win-game{{/if}}">{{p2_2}}</div>
      <div class="col-xs-4 {{#if p2_win_3}}win-game{{/if}}">{{p2_3}}</div>
    </div>
  <p>本项目已开源，详情请见 <a href="https://github.com/kitauji-gwent/kitauji-gwent" target="_blank">kitauji-gwent</a>.</p>
  <p>刷新页面可以重新开始比赛。</p>

  <div class="wrap-btn-action btn-register-action startMatchmaking" onclick="location.reload()">
    <input type="submit" value="再来一局" class="btn-action">
  </div>
  <p><b>Thanks for playing the game!</b></p>
</div>

<style>
  .startMatchmaking {
    line-height: 30px;
    width: auto;
    margin: 30px 0;
  }
  .score-row {
    margin-top: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .win-game {
    color: white;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
